 <title>Clean Air, Cool Climate: Solving these problems together</title>
 <link>http://www.chinafaqs.org/blog-posts/clean-air-cool-climate-solving-these-problems-together</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-filefield field-field-image&quot;&gt;
