 <title>U.S.-China S&amp;ED Outcomes Show Continued Progress on Climate Change Cooperation</title>
 <link>http://www.chinafaqs.org/blog-posts/us-china-sed-outcomes-show-continued-progress-climate-change-cooperation</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-filefield field-field-image&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;img src=&quot;http://www.chinafaqs.org/files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/US%20China%20meeting%20photo_2.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;180&quot; height=&quot;120&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default&quot;/&gt;        &lt;/div&gt;
